      <Project id="1083" parentID="1066" level="3" creatorID="0" sortOrder="0" createDate="2015-04-28T06:52:57" updateDate="2015-05-07T06:40:20" nodeName="Debt Tracker" urlName="debt-tracker" path="-1,1050,1066,1083" isDoc="" nodeType="1065" creatorName="Jon Stødle" writerName="Jon Stødle" writerID="0" template="1067" nodeTypeAlias="Project">
        <title><![CDATA[Debt Tracker]]></title>
        <description><![CDATA[<p id="yui_3_17_2_3_1430202316985_1209">Debt Tracker makes it easy to keep track of all the debts you have. No more paper notes or some virtual note on your phone or computer. This app makes it easy to add a person and all the related debts you have to that person. No more squabbling over who owes whom money and for what reason.</p>
<p>Debt Tracker is easy to understand and even easier to use. Adding persons and the debts related to them is simple and quick. And if the person should forget to pay you back, you can send a text message to remind you friend that he or she owes you money.</p>
<p>The easy integration with SkyDrive makes it possible to back up your data for safe keeping.</p>
<p>The ad banner is removable via in app purchase.</p>]]></description>
