        <title><![CDATA[Quote List]]></title>
        <description><![CDATA[<p id="yui_3_17_2_6_1430202316985_1147">Quote List let's you note down you favorite quotes, or just quotes you want to have handy in case you want to impress someone.</p>
<p>Quote List is designed to be fast and effective. The simple and fast interface of the app makes it easy to add and browse your saved quotes; no hassle, just ease of use.</p>
<p id="yui_3_17_2_6_1430202316985_1170">The trial version of Quote List let's you use the application with all it's features. By buying the app the ads that support the further development of the app will disappear.</p>]]></description>
